en: IIIF Canvas positioned in Scene multiple times with rotations

The Manifest has one Scene and one Canvas. Viewer should render what appears to be a ring of the same image (the Canvas) repeated multiple times. The viewer should respect the 'sequence' behavior on Range and not render a Scene and an independent Canvas.  https://i.etsystatic.com/9733435/r/il/7dbfe6/1879105213/il_fullxfull.1879105213_2xj3.jpg
